{
  "component": "atlas-checkbox",
  "type": "web-component",
  "description": "Checkbox para seleção binária ou múltipla com suporte a estados Default, Read-only, Disabled e Error",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "checked",
      "type": "boolean",
      "values": [true, false],
      "default": false,
      "required": false,
      "description": "Define se o checkbox está marcado"
    },
    {
      "name": "indeterminate",
      "type": "boolean",
      "values": [true, false],
      "default": false,
      "required": false,
      "description": "Estado intermediário para seleção parcial (pai com filhos parcialmente selecionados)"
    },
    {
      "name": "state",
      "type": "enum",
      "values": ["default", "read-only", "disabled", "error"],
      "default": "default",
      "required": false,
      "description": "Estado do checkbox: default (interativo), read-only (apenas leitura), disabled (desabilitado), error (erro de validação)"
    },
    {
      "name": "label",
      "type": "string",
      "values": [],
      "default": "",
      "required": false,
      "description": "Texto da label ao lado do checkbox"
    },
    {
      "name": "name",
      "type": "string",
      "values": [],
      "default": "",
      "required": false,
      "description": "Atributo name para formulários HTML"
    },
    {
      "name": "value",
      "type": "string",
      "values": [],
      "default": "",
      "required": false,
      "description": "Atributo value para formulários HTML"
    }
  ],
  "states": [
    {
      "name": "default-unchecked",
      "figma_tokens": {
        "background": "var(--atlas/color/surface/control/inactive/default, #fcfcfd)",
        "border": "var(--atlas/border/solid/default, 1px) solid var(--atlas/color/border/primary/hard, #0030b9)"
      },
      "icon": "nenhum",
      "behavior": "Estado padrão não marcado"
    },
    {
      "name": "default-checked",
      "figma_tokens": {
        "background": "SVG img6 (background preenchido)"
      },
      "icon": "check (✓)",
      "behavior": "Estado padrão marcado"
    },
    {
      "name": "default-indeterminate",
      "figma_tokens": {
        "background": "SVG img7 (background preenchido com minus)"
      },
      "icon": "minus (−)",
      "behavior": "Estado intermediário para seleção parcial"
    },
    {
      "name": "error-unchecked",
      "figma_tokens": {
        "background": "var(--atlas/color/surface/control/inactive/error, #fcfcfd)",
        "border": "var(--atlas/border/solid/default, 1px) solid var(--atlas/color/border/error/hard, #b02a37)"
      },
      "label_color": "var(--atlas/color/text/static/error/medium, #b02a37)",
      "icon": "nenhum",
      "behavior": "Estado de erro não marcado"
    },
    {
      "name": "error-checked",
      "figma_tokens": {
        "background": "SVG img4 (background preenchido)"
      },
      "label_color": "var(--atlas/color/text/static/error/medium, #b02a37)",
      "icon": "check (✓)",
      "behavior": "Estado de erro marcado"
    },
    {
      "name": "error-indeterminate",
      "figma_tokens": {
        "background": "SVG img5 (background preenchido com minus)"
      },
      "label_color": "var(--atlas/color/text/static/error/medium, #b02a37)",
      "icon": "minus (−)",
      "behavior": "Estado de erro intermediário"
    },
    {
      "name": "read-only-unchecked",
      "figma_tokens": {
        "background": "var(--atlas/color/surface/control/inactive/read-only, #fcfcfd)",
        "border": "var(--atlas/border/solid/default, 1px) solid var(--atlas/color/border/default, #d1d6dc)"
      },
      "icon": "nenhum",
      "behavior": "Apenas leitura não marcado"
    },
    {
      "name": "read-only-checked",
      "figma_tokens": {
        "background": "SVG img2 (background preenchido)"
      },
      "icon": "check (✓)",
      "behavior": "Apenas leitura marcado"
    },
    {
      "name": "read-only-indeterminate",
      "figma_tokens": {
        "background": "SVG img3 (background preenchido com minus)"
      },
      "icon": "minus (−)",
      "behavior": "Apenas leitura intermediário"
    },
    {
      "name": "disabled-unchecked",
      "figma_tokens": {
        "background": "var(--atlas/color/surface/control/inactive/disabled, #fcfcfd)",
        "border": "var(--atlas/border/solid/default, 1px) solid var(--atlas/color/border/disabled, #d1d6dc)"
      },
      "label_color": "var(--atlas/color/text/static/disabled/level-1, #d1d6dc)",
      "icon": "nenhum",
      "cursor": "not-allowed",
      "behavior": "Desabilitado não marcado - sem interação"
    },
    {
      "name": "disabled-checked",
      "figma_tokens": {
        "background": "SVG img (background preenchido cinza)"
      },
      "label_color": "var(--atlas/color/text/static/disabled/level-1, #d1d6dc)",
      "icon": "check (✓) cinza",
      "cursor": "not-allowed",
      "behavior": "Desabilitado marcado"
    },
    {
      "name": "disabled-indeterminate",
      "figma_tokens": {
        "background": "SVG img1 (background preenchido cinza com minus)"
      },
      "label_color": "var(--atlas/color/text/static/disabled/level-1, #d1d6dc)",
      "icon": "minus (−) cinza",
      "cursor": "not-allowed",
      "behavior": "Desabilitado intermediário"
    },
    {
      "name": "focus",
      "outline": "shadow-[0px_0px_0px_var(--atlas/focus/outline/size,2px)_var(--atlas/focus/outline/color,#3359c7)]",
      "outline_offset": "border-radius 6px",
      "behavior": "Outline de foco via teclado (:focus-visible)"
    }
  ],
  "layout": {
    "checkbox_size": "24px × 24px (container externo)",
    "content_size": "20px × 20px (box interno do checkbox)",
    "border_radius": "var(--atlas/radius/standalone/md, 4px)",
    "border_width": "var(--atlas/border/solid/default, 1px)",
    "gap": "var(--atlas/gap/xs, 8px) (entre checkbox e label)"
  },
  "typography": {
    "font_family": "var(--atlas/font-face/general, 'Open Sans')",
    "font_size": "var(--atlas/typescale/label/inline/md/size, 16px)",
    "font_weight": "var(--atlas/typescale/label/inline/md/weight/default, normal) = 400",
    "line_height": "1 (leading-none)",
    "letter_spacing": "var(--atlas/typescale/label/inline/md/letter-spacing, 0px)",
    "color_default": "var(--atlas/color/text/static/neutral/hard, #1d2125)",
    "color_error": "var(--atlas/color/text/static/error/medium, #b02a37)",
    "color_disabled": "var(--atlas/color/text/static/disabled/level-1, #d1d6dc)"
  },
  "icons": {
    "check": "SVG inline nos assets (img, img2, img4, img6)",
    "minus": "SVG inline nos assets (img1, img3, img5, img7)"
  },
  "variations": [
    {
      "description": "4 estados (Default, Error, Read-only, Disabled) × 3 variações (unchecked, checked, indeterminate)",
      "count": 12
    }
  ],
  "dependencies": [
    "../../tokens/atlas-design-tokens.css (tokens CSS do Figma)",
    "Google Fonts: Open Sans (400)"
  ],
  "figma": {
    "file": "https://www.figma.com/design/EpnFuPVWcjDYwkV2o2Vx3I/Atlas---UI-Kit",
    "component": "Checkbox default",
    "node-id": "119:478",
    "inspected": "2026-02-09",
    "documentation": "https://style.asaas.com/800892364/v/0/p/628992-checks-radios--switches/t/909e3d"
  },
  "notes": [
    "✅ TOKENS EXTRAÍDOS DO FIGMA:",
    "1. NÃO existe hover no checkbox (só focus-visible)",
    "2. Estados: Default, Error, Read-only, Disabled",
    "3. Variações: unchecked, checked, indeterminate (intermitate no Figma)",
    "4. Label muda de cor em Error (#b02a37) e Disabled (#d1d6dc)",
    "5. Border width: 1px (var(--atlas/border/solid/default))",
    "6. Focus: shadow com 2px em #3359c7",
    "7. Ícones vêm como SVG inline (não fonte de ícones)",
    "",
    "⚠️ ALERTA: SVG ASSETS NÃO DISPONÍVEIS:",
    "O Figma retornou SVGs como localhost URLs que não são acessíveis.",
    "Alternativa: Usar atlas-icon component com glyphs 'check' e 'minus'",
    "",
    "IMPLEMENTAÇÃO:",
    "- Use <input type='checkbox'> com appearance: none",
    "- SVG inline OU atlas-icon com glyph='check' / glyph='minus'",
    "- Focus: usar :focus-visible (não :focus)",
    "- Indeterminate: setar via JS → input.indeterminate = true",
    "- aria-checked='mixed' para indeterminate"
  ]
}
